    "description": "Hokuriku Electric Industry Co.,Ltd. engages in the development, manufacturing, and sale of electronic components in Japan and internationally. The company offers force sensors, pressure sensors, pressure sensor module, and humidity sensors element and module; circuit modules; piezoelectric sounder and buzzers; high function chip fixed resistors; chip fixed resistors; and network chip fixed resistors. It also provides metal plate chip fixed resistors; fixed metal film resistors; fixed metal oxide film resistors; chip type cermet trimmer potentiometer and miniature cermet trimmer potentiometers variable resistors; NTC thermistor; tactile switches; and printed circuit boards. The company also provides fixed metal film, fixed metal oxide film, and fixed carbon film resistors; chip type and miniature cermet trimmer potentiometers; glass sealed radial lead, glass sealed axial lead, and epoxy resin coated radial lead thermistors; tactile switches; and printed circuit boards. Its products are used in mobile communication, digital appliance/PC, car electronics, and home electronic applications. The company was incorporated in 1943 and is based in Toyama, Japan."
